# SPEC: Facilities & CEO System v5.6

## Status: ✅ IMPLEMENTED

## Overview
Economic production system with 13 facilities across 5 sectors, facility construction/upgrade, service revenue, tech tree viewer, and CEO company creation with sector selection.

